text: Jeon Sae-yan (born ) is a South Korean female volleyball player. She is part of the South Korea women's national volleyball team. == Career == She participated at the 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Grand Champions Cup. == Clubs == * Korea Expressway Corporation, 2017 == References == == External links == * FIVB Profile * Coppa KOVO F.: Trofeo alle GS Caltex di Diouck * Tokio, Japan.
